1041
00:59:08.660 --> 00:59:12.240
And I hope it also convinces you that even when we don't have the full tissue

1042
00:59:12.280 --> 00:59:16.060
section, because that is not clinically feasible, we learn quite a bit.

1043
00:59:17.040 --> 00:59:20.730
So, very briefly, we've conducted a number of

1044
00:59:20.730 --> 00:59:24.250
studies with wonderful clinician scientists, looking

1045
00:59:24.460 --> 00:59:28.360
at repeat sampling throughout either targeted therapy, in this case, in the

1046
00:59:28.400 --> 00:59:31.920
context of anti-HER2, in this TRIO-USB07 study.

1047
00:59:32.420 --> 00:59:36.110
And in this study, we had a pre-treatment biopsy and on-treatment biopsy without

1048
00:59:36.160 --> 00:59:38.860
chemo, which is really remarkable. It was just trastuzumab.

