01:03:46.660 --> 01:03:50.400
compared to, let's say, the typical risk tumors down

1122
01:03:50.460 --> 01:03:52.600
here or triple negative, they're immune depleted.

1123
01:03:53.420 --> 01:03:56.950
And what's intriguing is, I won't show it here, but you could read about it in this

1124
01:03:56.960 --> 01:04:00.800
publication. If you map these patients at a genome-wide level

1125
01:04:00.860 --> 01:04:03.700
using whole genome sequencing and reconstruct their

