01:05:32.800 --> 01:05:36.390
data. You'll see pretty good representation of myeloid cells.

1153
01:05:36.420 --> 01:05:40.180
Pretty striking depletion of lymphoid, but we can also pick a number of

1154
01:05:40.220 --> 01:05:41.460
different stromal compartments.

1155
01:05:42.160 --> 01:05:46.120
And again, we can do a very deep dive into all these

1156
01:05:46.140 --> 01:05:49.320
different patterns of cell-cell communication and colocalization.

