01:07:21.256 --> 01:07:24.526
we see this pretty dramatic separation in patient outcomes.

1185
01:07:24.556 --> 01:07:26.856
So these are patients that have niche zero.

1186
01:07:26.896 --> 01:07:30.316
They have very poor prognosis. But what's exciting

1187
01:07:30.916 --> 01:07:34.096
is that I previously told you we could predict 20 years risk of relapse from our

