01:08:04.816 --> 01:08:08.595
This is the first time we've really been able to demonstrate this.

1199
01:08:09.796 --> 01:08:12.576
So I can come back to the co-localization that I showed you.

1200
01:08:13.196 --> 01:08:16.337
There's these different groupings of cancer epithelial cells.

