01:25:06.012 --> 01:25:09.812
typical risk lesion? And a lot of that follows what we know about grading,

1509
01:25:09.892 --> 01:25:12.372
staging, pathology. We don't want to omit that information.

1510
01:25:12.392 --> 01:25:12.402
Right.

1511
01:25:12.402 --> 01:25:13.052
It's so rich.

1512
01:25:14.452 --> 01:25:14.602
So

