01:25:15.412 --> 01:25:18.482
what I would stress, the reason I showed the H&amp;E at the fore, although I didn't

1514
01:25:18.512 --> 01:25:22.012
talk about is, without that grounding, I think we could be misleading ourselves.

1515
01:25:22.042 --> 01:25:25.192
And we will also really struggle to scale any of these tools at a population level.

1516
01:25:25.292 --> 01:25:29.072
So one of our big tasks is now we can make measurements on FFP tissue

1517
01:25:29.812 --> 01:25:33.572
